How to use the Framer components

✓ Your components are exported to framer folder

Each component has a .Responsive variant that allows you to
specify different variants for different breakpoints.

You can use the components like this:
(try copy pasting the code below into your React app)

import './framer/styles.css'

import TabsContentFramerComponent from './framer/tabs-content'
import NavigationFramerComponent from './framer/navigation'
import TopContentFramerComponent from './framer/top-content'
